text: Liliya Stoyanova (born 19 November 1968) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed in the women's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Sofia
